			<Text>Go on a great Hajj, spending {2_InstantYield} to unlock the Adobe Mosque Building. Other Mosques generate +3 [ICON_GOLDEN_AGE] Golden Age Points.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_EVENT_SONGHAI_UE_HELP_CHOICE_4">
			<Text>Spend {2_InstantYield} in order to protect 2 copies of [ICON_RES_GOLD] Gold. Your Constabularies boost [ICON_GOLD] Gold income by 5%.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_EVENT_SONGHAI_UE_HELP_CHOICE_5">
			<Text>Pour {2_InstantYield} worth of resources into the [ICON_RES_OIL] Oil sector, gaining 5 copies and gaining +3 [ICON_GOLD] Gold, [ICON_PRODUCTION] Production and [ICON_GOLDEN_AGE] Golden Age Points from every Well and Offshore Platform.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_EVENT_SONGHAI_UE_HELP_CHOICE_6">
			<Text>Implement widespread policies to combat climate change. Cities gain +2 [ICON_RESEARCH] Science, [ICON_FOOD] Food and [ICON_TOURISM] Tourism for every Desert Tile.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_EVENT_SONGHAI_UE_DESCRIPTION_CHOICE_1">
			<Text>People need a role model, to know what is a worthy life. Bring me our brightest student, I will shower him with gifts in front of all Songhai.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_EVENT_SONGHAI_UE_DESCRIPTION_CHOICE_2">
			<Text>*Slavery has become widespread, but the lack of a clear legal infrastructure means these men answer to neither you nor God*[NEWLINE]I will show my generosity first to the slaves, by defining who can be bought and sold and how they must be treated. Then I will show my generosity to the slavers, by giving them a square in every City to do their trade.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_EVENT_SONGHAI_UE_DESCRIPTION_CHOICE_3">
			<Text>*The clerics of the Grand Temple wish for you to perform an act that will show that all glory goes to God, beyond all doubt*[NEWLINE]I take no offense to this request, as it is just and holy. I will give a large portion of my wealth to the poor, as I travel to the holy city of the faith!</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_EVENT_SONGHAI_UE_DESCRIPTION_CHOICE_4">
			<Text>*We are rich, but the mercurial and fleeting nature of wealth concerns us deeply*[NEWLINE]To squander God's gifts is a great disgrace. We safeguard our wealth in Gold, and be ever vigilant in the protection of the sources of our prosperity.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_EVENT_SONGHAI_UE_DESCRIPTION_CHOICE_5">
			<Text>*This black gold - oil - that can be found deep below the Empire is precious above all previous resources*[NEWLINE]Just as we sook to protect the sources of our affluence in the past, so to must we adapt going into the future. This oil is a gift from God, that is certain.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_EVENT_SONGHAI_UE_DESCRIPTION_CHOICE_6">
			<Text>*The planet changes and the deserts threaten to encroach upon land that was previously fertile*[NEWLINE]We have brought this doom upon us, it is up to us to fix it. We must live, love and learn about our Earth, or we shall surely perish.</Text>
		</Row>
